# Task Management API

A Node.js-based RESTful API for user authentication and task management.

## 🚀 Features

- User registration and login (JWT-based authentication)
- Task creation, retrieval, updating, and deletion
- Middleware for authentication
- Modular folder structure (MVC-based)

## 🧾 Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (via Mongoose)
- JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
- Dotenv

## 📁 Project Structure

```
task-management/
├── .env
├── app.js
├── controllers/
│   ├── authController.js
│   └── taskController.js
├── models/
│   ├── User.js
│   └── Task.js
├── routes/
│   ├── authRoutes.js
│   └── taskRoutes.js
└── utils/
